<template><div><h1 id="isobject" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#isobject" aria-hidden="true">#</a> isobject <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/isobject" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/npm/v/isobject.svg?style=flat" alt="NPM version"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a> <a href="https://npmjs.org/package/isobject" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/npm/dm/isobject.svg?style=flat" alt="NPM monthly downloads"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a>  <a href="https://npmjs.org/package/isobject" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/npm/dt/isobject.svg?style=flat" alt="NPM total downloads"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a> <a href="https://travis-ci.org/jonschlinkert/isobject" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/travis/jonschlinkert/isobject.svg?style=flat&amp;label=Travis" alt="Linux Build Status"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a></h1>
<blockquote>
<p>Returns true if the value is an object and not an array or null.</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="install" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#install" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Install</h2>
<p>Install with <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">npm<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>:</p>
<div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> --save isobject
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>Install with <a href="https://yarnpkg.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">yarn<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>:</p>
<div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">yarn</span> <span class="token function">add</span> isobject
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>Use <a href="https://github.com/jonschlinkert/is-plain-object" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">is-plain-object<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> if you want only objects that are created by the <code v-pre>Object</code> constructor.</p>
<h2 id="install-1" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#install-1" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Install</h2>
<p>Install with <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">npm<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>:</p>
<div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> isobject
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>Install with <a href="https://bower.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">bower<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></p>
<div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-bash"><code>$ bower <span class="token function">install</span> isobject
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="usage" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#usage" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Usage</h2>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">var</span> isObject <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token function">require</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'isobject'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>True</strong></p>
